game.name: Baby Around The World Russia
game.description:
Is going on a trip around the world your big dream of the life? If yes, then you must explore this brand new game: Baby Around The World Russia where you will get a chance to travel the entire world with a beautiful girl Jessy, who is also crazy for visiting and roaming various beautiful locations all across the globe. Her trip will start with a plenty of exotic places of Russia. Play this cool kitchen game and help Jessy to learn and explore the rich and beautiful culture of Russia, especially their popular cuisine.

This cute baby girl wants to know the all the little and big things about this amazing country in this free online cooking game for girls. Join her to make her trip wonderful and memorable for the rest of her life. In her first task, she wants to cook something special since learning how to cook delicious food is a viable key to know a country closely. Take a bowl and mix some water, a pinch of salt, biscuits, eggs, honey, sugar and flow in it. Roll the dough and then slice it into rounded shapes. Use another bowl and mix some strawberry jam, cloves, cardamom, cinnamon and ginger into it. 

Use this mixture to fill your dough. Once it is done, place another piece of dough on top and mold it in a rose shape. You will get a nice Russian dessert after putting it into the oven for a while. After preparing the dessert, help the baby to select a right traditional Russian costume with vivid colors and flower prints. Color the background: Kremlin building on your own using your creativity skills. Play this one of the best cooking games for kids and have fun a lot!
